title: Zeitning Round 2/7: Lt Col Vindman, Pete's Billionaires, Ke$ha, Swagger, Pod Save America
itunes:title: Zeitning Round 2/7: Lt Col Vindman, Pete's Billionaires, Ke$ha, Swagger, Pod Save America
description:
On this edition of Zeitning Round Jack, Jamie, and DJ Danl discuss Lt Col Vindman getting escorted out of the Whitehouse, the "Pete's Billionaires" meme, another unfortunate development in the case between Ke$ha and Dr Luke, the passing of "Swagger" the mascot for Cleveland Browns, and the Pod Save America hosts may know more about SHADOW than we thought!
